description: Performs FlowSOM (cluster n=15) and views the results with a heatmap and minimum spanning tree (MST). FlowSOM clusters are also visualized in a heatmap using MEM score. 2D plot with Flt-SNE and UMAP.  FlowSOM and UMAP results will be stored in the exporting data folder for the further application. No downsampling applied. For use with FlowJo plugin uploaded data.
name: FlowJo Cluster Explorer - Full
